devdoc.author: Gustavo Henrique / gustavo@useinsignia.com

addNewDoc(string,string,string,string,st.details: The owner of the contract could insert a fee to publish data, default 0 , e.g. 100 = 1%

params._docProcess: The string to retrieve the data, should be related to the context of the documentation
params._docsURI: The IPFS CID of the tree documentation  e.g. Auction_Docs
params._docsURIChesksum: The hash of the tree documentation, certify the integrity of the data
params._publisherResponsible: The responsible for publishing the documentation

constructor.details: Sets the values for :  {minimunFee} -> The fee charged on every new document added

returns._0: uint of the total native token balance

params.enable: True to guarantee privilegies, false to remove privilegies

devdoc.title: Vault for store real estate documents
